        <h3 id="query">Query API</h3>
        <p>
	  ADBC published a <a href="https://github.com/ausdigital/adbc/raw/master/Digital_Capability_Locator_Implementation_Guide_v1.0.pdf">DCL Implementation Guide</a> with query API and management API parts. The Testpoint DCL implementation complies with the query API.
	</p>
	<p>
	  Submit well formed NAPTR queries to DNS at *.dcl.testpoint.io
	</p>
      </div>
      
      <div id="home-tabs-management" class="tabs-content">
        <h3 id="management">Management API</h3>
        <p>
          ADBC published a <a href="https://github.com/ausdigital/adbc/raw/master/Digital_Capability_Locator_Implementation_Guide_v1.0.pdf">DCL Implementation Guide</a> with query API and management API parts. The Testpoint DCL implemetation does not yet comply with the proposed Management API, however a simplified management interface is provides which is adequate for many testing and development purposes.
        </p>
	<p>
	  To use the simplified management interface:
	  <ol>
	    <li>Click the "Login with idp.testpoint.io" link at the top right of the page.</li>
	    <li>Then select the "Update SMP" link at the top right of the page.</li>
	    <li>Then fill in the form and click "submit".</li>
	  </ol>
	  This requires that you log in with ABN credentials that have been configured with the <a href="http://idp.testpoint.io/">Testpoint IDP</a>
	</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
